Sigh I always seem to update when I am feeling down, right now I am just sitting here not wanting to deal with another living soul for as long as can, but it never seems too last long enough.  At least school is out but then that brings up a bunch of worries such as if I should take summer class, my SUCK ASS FUCKING job, my friends, my girlfriend and Sigma Pi.  For some reason I have lost my will to try in life, it feel like a hole has ripped open inside of me like an old wound that never healed and is slowing devouring me.  I have lost my motivation for life, I mean the only reason I even tried to pass high school was for my parent because honestly I didnt care and right now I still dont and I relied on my girlfriend to get through this year at wayne but I am soo tired to using others as my motivation in life and I just cant seem to find anything else because I dont care about my feelings and well being.  To me a life without my friend and family is like suffering and I should be put out of my misery.  and just seems like I can do better and try harder to make the better grade and to do this and to do that, but I just dont care anymore. I just feel like crawling into the darkness and giving up. I just wish I could be the person every thinks I am, and sometimes I wonder how much they know me, I wonder if I even know myself. 

-Hurt-NIN
